    {
        "Id": 6,
        "ActionId": 551,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": "DialogEnable",
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: 'I hacked into a mechanoid\\'s memory shell, but the data I got so far only reveals the authority hierarchy on the ship.', 4: '3'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 7,
        "ActionId": 552,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Lee', 3: 'It\\'s based on biometric verification. Organism, or in this case humans, have the lowest authority on the ship, followed by mechanoids, then Constructs. The highest authority belongs to the main control system.', 4: '3'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 8,
        "ActionId": 553,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'A sad look creeps onto Liv\\'s face, as if she is reminded of something unpleasant.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 9,
        "ActionId": 554,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Lee', 3: 'The \"Pulao crew\" that the merchant are a group of people serving under someone called Pulao. Pulao is a member of the Kowloong Crew, the other members include Qiuniu, Yazi, Chaofeng, Suanni, Baxia, Bian, Fuxi, and Chiwen.', 4: '3'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 10,
        "ActionId": 555,
        "NextActionId": 6,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Lee', 3: 'These are the code names of the Kowloong Crew Constructs on the ship. They have mid-level authority.', 4: '3'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 11,
        "ActionId": 6,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: '...I should also mention that these mechanoids have virtual M.I.N.D.s and they function normally.', 4: '3'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 12,
        "ActionId": 7,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 302,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Virtual M.I.N.D.s?', 3: '8', 4: 'Function normally?', 5: '10'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 13,
        "ActionId": 8,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Lee', 3: 'They can engage in rudimentary thinking and thought simulation. Compared with Construct M.I.N.D.s, mechanoid M.I.N.D.s simulate reality more precisely. They should also be capable of consciousness recall.', 4: '3'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 14,
        "ActionId": 9,
        "NextActionId": 11,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Lee', 3: 'Well, \"consciousness\"... as in recalling their info storage and holographic data.', 4: '3'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 15,
        "ActionId": 10,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Lee', 3: 'They can think on a rudimentary level and simulate thought. They\\'re also capable of consciousness recall.', 4: '3'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 16,
        "ActionId": 11,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Lee', 3: 'This is part of the reason why you were able to link with and manipulate them...', 4: '3'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 17,
        "ActionId": 12,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Lee', 3: 'Meanwhile, I checked the control terminals in this place too... They\\'re rather advanced.', 4: '3'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 18,
        "ActionId": 111,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 204,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '2', 2: '14'}"
    },
    {
